#Science ? #Biology ? #Microbiology ? Naaaah. Just some #cgi shit. Pdgradplay v1 avg snap. So, this is pretty simple actually. I’m calculating local point density. And using the gradient of that to push the points. With some sin and cos. But no noise. Also I used point relax first to avoid points getting too close but it was tooo slow, so I used fuse and reversed it to get a similar effect and it was way faster. #houdini #offspring @offspring #animation #creativecoding #generativeart #art @sidefxhoudini

1. Please please please share this if you can. 2. This is the only job that never paid me. I did this for @bangbangnyc in june of 2022. They never paid me. They offered a possible 50% payment because they never used the piece. They never told me they’re not happy with the job at the time I finished the project. A guy named Jesse McGowan was in charge of the project. I’ve done many freelance jobs and people usually are honest and pay on time but these guys just refused to pay and the worst part is that they stopped answering my emails. Very disrespectful. I asked them many times to at least let me know if they don’t wanna pay so I can at least do something about it. Anyway, if you’re an artist watch out for these guys. And if you know a good lawyer that isn’t more expensive than an average freelance job payment please let me know ;) cheers! #bangbangtattoo #bangbang #tattoo #cgart
